title: Kathleen Woodiwiss_Come Love a Stranger
description: Lierin -- With no name and no memory, she awakens from a nightmare of madness into the lives of two strangers. One she desires, one she fears -- but both have claimed her heart. To handsome plantation owner Ashton Wingate, she is "Lierin" -- the cherished bride cruelly stolen from him by capricious Fate. The other calls her "Lenore" -- entangling the lost, tormented beauty in his sinister web of perilous deceit. But it is in the adoring arms of noble Ashton that her true destiny awaits -- as they join together to unlock the mysteries of a shadowed past... and to rekindle the flames of a glorious love once vanished but never forgotten..
